{"tid":2278004,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"有冇人可以講吓其實基督教嘅福音派同基要派有咩分別","createTime":"2020-11-09T01:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T13:32:57.000Z","uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"327972c96b3b5d336f0b24db6eeaaefc3009397f","tid":2278004,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:08:34.000Z","msg":"一直以來淨係覺得基督教嘅派別分咗兩種<br />\n比較痴線小小嘅靈恩派<br />\n同埋着重聖經嘅福音基要派<br />\n但係<br />\n真係唔清楚其實福音牌同基要派究竟有咩唔同<br />\n有冇基督徒巴絲可以分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d6253caabb1ee6e943ef096aadbab4b6d581b3","tid":2278004,"uid":271714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:33:43.000Z","msg":"Wiki: <br />\nBarry Hankins (2008) has a similar view, saying &quot;beginning in the 1940s....militant and separatist evangelicals came to be called fundamentalists, while culturally engaged and non-militant evangelicals were supposed to be called evangelicals.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n大概係話願意融入社會、冇咁軍事化嘅就係福音派，軍事化管理、從社會疏離嘅就係基要派"},{"pid":"c0c0c08265686866228e026ce2665ae46415f06f","tid":2278004,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:25:10.000Z","msg":"從教義光譜嚟講<br />\n基要派掀開本聖經，文字寫乜就信乜，話神用咗七日創世就係用咗7x24小時，唔會有錯。<br />\n福音派就係主流最多人嘅宗派，教義上有啲走盞位，例如七日創世佢哋會詮釋為比喻緊七個階段，每個階段可以有幾億萬年，嗱係咪符合科學呀。但大部分都相信聖經無誤。香港應該絕大部分教會都係福音派。<br />\n重有個自由派，可以接受聖經有錯同創作成份，甚至耶穌唔存在都得，相信世界終極存在係至善全能嘅神。不過數量極少。<br />\n靈恩派就另一種，教義唔清楚，主流通常都當佢哋異端。啲通靈效果我認為係心理作用，或者有啲靈體同佢哋交流，畢竟呢個世界好多靈。<br />\n以上全憑印象同主觀意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0f18ef5fd8e33c2cd790ef4cfd8ae77a3f2298","tid":2278004,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"咁錫安教會係咩派"},{"pid":"894376ea90869f8be98d3633bbabba4b6720d48b","tid":2278004,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:32:25.000Z","msg":"睇返wiki我啲terms有啲亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面講「自由派」係09年左右, 香港網民搞遊行𨳒柒啲宗教霸權<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/維護公民社會價值，反對宗教右翼霸權大遊行\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E5%8F%B3%E7%BF%BC%E9%9C%B8%E6%AC%8A%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=85b2c2f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/維護公民社會價值，反對宗教右翼霸權大遊行</a><br />\n嗰期有班基督徒出嚟講返基督教都有自由派, 同意聖經有錯漏, 接受同性戀等等<br />\n當中可能夾雜咗啲 一位論派(unitarianism) 思想, 我上面撈亂咗<br />\n呢班自稱自由派嘅人而家唔知重有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過嗰次之後啲宗教右派都收晒皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/自由主義神學\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9%E7%A5%9E%E5%AD%B8&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=8172f202\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/自由主義神學</a><br />\n所謂自由派, 應該係去到近代, 啲人睇返聖經唔對路, 搞出咗 <br />\n自由主義神學(Liberal Christianity), 新自由主義神學 之類嚟修正. 睇返入面都好多翼思想. 同埋太自由難以歸納其定義. <br />\n不過呢啲係學術佬神學, 現實中各教會有冇採納呢啲觀點去詮釋教義, 並且信受奉行就唔知了. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/基督教基要主義\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E5%9F%BA%E7%9D%A3%E6%95%99%E5%9F%BA%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=d7052a7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/基督教基要主義</a><br />\n然後有班保守撚唔接受, 搞咗個基要主義嚟對抗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/福音派\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E6%B4%BE&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=d5ef54d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/福音派</a><br />\n最初嘅新教自稱福音派<br />\n<blockquote>在16世紀宗教改革時期，馬丁&middot;路德的跟隨者，自稱「福音派」</blockquote><br />\n然後受到自由派思想衝擊<br />\n然後出現基要主義<br />\n<blockquote>從1940年開始，福音主義在基督教基要主義中興起。基要主義慢慢分化出正式的基要派和福音派。</blockquote><br />\n即係一個原教旨主義, 一個保守得嚟講下道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a65ace25c3b18232892718a3e91843947b2330","tid":2278004,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb0f18ef5fd8e33c2cd790ef4cfd8ae77a3f2298","tid":2278004,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"咁錫安教會係咩派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:32:57.000Z","msg":"異端, 異端, 全部都係異端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}